        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Cardiomyopathy Health Education, Awareness, Research, and Training in the Schools Act of 2017</strong><strong> or HEARTS Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a series of programs and requirements relating to cardiomyopathy, including school awareness campaigns and research initiatives.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
